videos.description: With a tie game between Northeastern and Oakland and under 10 seconds left in regulation, Huskies G T.J. Williams dribbles downcourt toward the basket and puts up a game-winning shot while falling to the ground.
videos.headline: Northeastern's Williams wins it at the buzzer
